imdb.plot outline: A stone s throw away from London, the Cat Survival Trust has the largest collection of snow leopards. This is an observational documentary that captures intimate never-seen-before footage of snow leopards. We'll find out just what goes into rearing new-born snow leopards, the day to day work of the Trust, its other cat residents and ground-breaking conservation plans for the future.
